{"tid":2379688,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"去年7.1兩名學生被控拒捕及阻差辦公，控方今加控三人暴動罪 !","createTime":"2021-01-25T11:27:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-25T11:28:11.000Z","uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"32e50fdf20845bbb469b76910663c9285ff6cab6","tid":2379688,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T11:27:31.000Z","msg":"去年7.1警方在銅鑼灣驅散聚集市民，其間一名工程師涉用利器刺傷防暴警左臂，被控蓄意傷人罪，另有兩名學生因事件而被控拒捕及阻差辦公。控方今加控三人暴動罪，兩案將轉介區域法院審理，押後至3月1日在東區法院再訊，以待準備轉介文件。<br />\n<br />\n工程師黃鈞華（24歲）被指去年7月1日在銅鑼灣皇仁書院外意圖使警員25116身體受嚴重傷害，而非法及惡意傷害該警員，又被指於同日在銅鑼灣高士威道一帶與羅姓男生、周霈霖及其他身份不明人士參與暴動。被告沒有申請保釋，繼續還柙候訊。<br />\n<br />\n另一案被告為羅姓男生（17歲）及周霈霖（19歲），二人分別被指於去年7月1日在銅鑼灣皇仁書院外抗拒及阻撓警員25116，並在銅鑼灣高士威道一帶與黃鈞華及其他身份不明人士參與暴動。二人獲准繼續以原有條件保釋。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210125/JDMXEAUQBFDALKHRGXNNM2QCUI/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR13kJuafdjKjccKxKb2kqTqVsmIGGkAZpy-IjTC9yTjuedpVrAZsgKv3CM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210125%2FJDMXEAUQBFDALKHRGXNNM2QCUI%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR13kJuafdjKjccKxKb2kqTqVsmIGGkAZpy-IjTC9yTjuedpVrAZsgKv3CM&d=Bi029C%2FGDe0wU7DInIQABQV2WuQOZSh7uXaWrws9Zz8%3D&h=64574ce8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210125%2FJDMXEAUQBFDALKHRGXNNM2QCUI%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR13kJuafdjKjccKxKb2kqTqVsmIGGkAZpy-IjTC9yTjuedpVrAZsgKv3CM&h=fd20b5cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210125/JDMXEAUQBFDALKHRGXNNM2QCUI/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR13kJuafdjKjccKxKb2kqTqVsmIGGkAZpy-IjTC9yTjuedpV